divs: Sighting DetailsObject spoted north of McKInney about 7:20 pm on May-02-08 The picture of the object - which I refered to as maybe a jet plane and vapor trail, was not the object I saw. But was taken almost imediatlly after I lost sight of the origanal object. The picture was of an object traveling from south to north. It seem intresting enough to post as it did not quite look like a jet. And it was at a high altitude. I am going to take some pictures of jets with cem-trails and see if it is just my camera making them look like that or maybe she did take a picture of something different.
Summary: McKinney Re - white sphere traveling from north to south
